spx.av

Class SrcType

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.av.SrcType

  • public class SrcType
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains constants that match the enumeration values of the SPxAVSrcType enum from SPxAVSvrStream.h and functions to convert a capture source type to a string.
